Usage: createGAFillerGroup [-help] -ga_cells <ga cell list>
                           -ga_fillers <ga filler cell list> -group <groupName>

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-ga_cells <ga cell list>              # GA cell list (string, required)
-ga_fillers <ga filler cell list>     # GA filler cell list (string, required)
-group <groupName>                    # GA group name (string, required)